{"id": "sos012", "name": "Audio_Sagar_702_11_29", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Scan_01", "Signal Transmission"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Sagar]"], "content": "<i>Calling Big B. What are you doing?</i>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "...eh, Captain? \nNothing. Just analyzing some old codes.\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Sagar]"], "content": "<i>Need help? I can arrange for some guys...</i>\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "Almost finished. No worries.\nWe meeting up?\n\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Sagar]"], "content": "<i>Already been 3 minutes... It's not like you to forget.</i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "... Damnit... be right there!\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»Fast Forward»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "Big B, what the hell you doing? Squad meeting! You can't just do whatever the f*** you want.\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "Look who's talking.\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "Sorry to make you all wait... Captain.\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Alright, everybody listen up.\nI've gotten news from HQ that the mission's changed.\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Exploration Team Member T"], "content": "Changed? We don't need to arrest the target anymore?\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "No, the target hasn't changed. But \"bring him back dead or alive\" has changed to \"it's absolutely necessary that he be brought back alive\".\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "WHAT!?\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "... What's the matter, Alex?\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "Are you kidding me? This ain't gonna be any fun!\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "... Captain, considering how dangerous the target is, it's going to extremely difficult to capture him alive. Much more so than shooting him dead. We're going to need a major strategy adjustment.\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Exploration Team Member K"], "content": "I agree. The report on the watch shop owner indicated that the target lives deep in the forbidden areas. It'll take us 2 weeks just to get there... the environment's already dangerous enough, now we've got to think of a way to capture the target alive?\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "I know this'll increase our workload, but we're Eagle-01's cream of the crop. I trust it won't be an issue.\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "Oh, shut it, Bambi! I want out of this boring s***!\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "Jackal!\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Relax, Lucy.\n... Alex, we've got to catch him alive, but I've got a mission I want to give you.\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "Eh?\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Whether or not he sees it coming, once we find the guy... You're going to smash his right arm.\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "... Oh...\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Lucy, you're going to use a stun gun to short circuit his right eye. If he loses half of his vision and use of his right arm, his sense of balance will go out of wack. There's no way he'll be able to move with any control.\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "So, injuring him isn't an issue?\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "That's right.\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "... Hey, you really want to get this guy, huh?\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Of course.\nWhatta you think? You want it?\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "Cut the s***! This mission's mine!\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Great. Let's discuss the details.\nEveryone else get back in position.\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "Footsteps"], "content": ""}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "... Strange.\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "Really? Captain's plan sounds right on point...\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "I mean you...\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "... Me?\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "When Captain issued the command, everyone was surprised. You were the only one who maintained a straight face. Almost like you knew what HQ was planning before we did.\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "... You're overthinking it.\nI've felt like this fugitive was something special since the very beginning. You think A.R.C. would send the entire team of elites just to catch a simple fugitive? There's something more going on. \n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "So, you expected something like this to happen?\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "In any case, I'm the Captain's primary advisor.\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "Are you on edge for Sagar's sake? Relax. I worked with Alex and Sagar before you even joined the squad.\nHaha... lots of memories.\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "He told me about Jackal.\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "Then you oughta hear what happened later... Sagar would happily tell you. He's got a thing for you, after all.\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "... As a member of the team.\nI'll leave you be.\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "Footsteps"], "content": ""}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Scan_01", "シグナル転送"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Sagar]"], "content": "<i>ビッグB。どこで何をしてる？</i>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "……あ、隊長か？\nいや、古いコードを分析してるだけだ。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Sagar]"], "content": "<i>人手はいるか？\n必要なら誰か……</i>\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "いや、もう終わるからいい。\nもう集合の時間か？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Sagar]"], "content": "<i>もう3分過ぎてるぞ……時間を忘れるなんてお前らしくない。</i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "……やべ……今すぐ行く！\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "ビッグB、お前いったい何してたんだよ？\n全員がお前の事待ってたんだぜ？\n勝手な行動されちゃ困るんだよな～\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "あんたにそれを言う資格はない。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "悪い、みんな……待たせたな。\n……隊長。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "よし。全員よく聞くんだ。\n本部から任務変更の指令を受け取った。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["探査隊員 T"], "content": "変更？ターゲットを追わなくていいって事か？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "いや、ターゲットは変わらない。\nだが、元は「生死は問わない」だったが、「生きて捕らえよ」とのことだ。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "はぁ！？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……何か不満か？Alex。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "ふざけんなよ！\nくそつまんねーじゃん！\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "……隊長。\nターゲットの危険性を考えると、生きて捕らえる方が射殺するよりずっと難しい。\n作戦を変更しよう。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["探査隊員 K"], "content": "私も同意です。\n時計屋の店主の情報から見ても、ターゲットは封鎖エリアの奥深くにいると考えられます。\nここからターゲットの位置まで移動するだけで2週間……\nそうでなくとも危険な環境下での任務です。\nその上生け捕りですか？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "みんなの負担が増えることは分かっている。\nだが、ここにいるみんなはEagle-01の優秀な隊員たちだ。\nきっとできると俺は信じている。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "おいおい、バンビいい加減にしろよ！\nこんなクソ任務俺はおりるからな！\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "ジャッカル！\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Lucy、いい。\n……Alex、ターゲットを生け捕りにする任務は変わらない。\nだが、お前に任せたい任務がある。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "んあ？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "ターゲットを発見次第、相手の抵抗の意思の有無に拘わらず……右手を破壊しろ。\n徹底的にだ。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "……おお……\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "同時に、Lucy。\nお前は電撃弾でターゲットの右目をショートさせるんだ。\n片目の視力と片腕を失えば、バランス感覚を失い思うように動けなくなる。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "ケガさせてもいいって事だな？\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "あぁ、構わない。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "……へぇ、マジであいつを捕まえたいんだ？\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "当たり前だ。\nどうだ？やるか？\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "決まってんだろ！奴の右腕をぶっ壊すのはこの俺様だ！\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "ならいい。\nよし、細かい作戦をたてよう。\n他のみんなは持ち場に戻ってくれ。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "足音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "……おかしい。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "そうか？隊長の配置は間違ってないと思うが……\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "おかしいのはあんた。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "……俺？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "隊長が任務の変更をみんなに伝えた時、みんなは驚いていたのにあんただけ平然としてた。\nまるで本部がこの命令を下すことが最初から分かってたみたいに。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "……考えすぎだ。\n俺は最初から今回の任務は簡単にはいかないと思ってた。\nA.R.C.の精鋭部隊である俺たちが全員出動してるんだぞ？\nたった一人の指名手配犯を捕まえるために。\n間違いなく何かが裏に隠されてる。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "つまり、こうなることが最初から分かっていたと？\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "俺だってだてに隊長の参謀を務めてるわけじゃない。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "お前はSagarのことを思ってそこまで警戒してるんだろ？\n安心しろ。\nお前が入ってくる前から、俺とAlexは隊長と組んでるんだ。\nはは……懐かしいな。\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "ジャッカルとの話は聞いた事がある。\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "なら、その後の話も聞いてみるべきだ……Sagarはきっと喜んで話してくれるぜ？\nお前のことは気に入ってるみたいだからな。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "……それは隊員としての話。\nじゃ、もう行くから。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "足音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Scan_01", "訊號傳輸"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Sagar]"], "content": "<i>呼叫大 B。你在做什麼？</i>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "……啊，隊長？\n沒什麼，我在分析一些舊編碼。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Sagar]"], "content": "<i>需要幫忙嗎？我可以安排人手……</i>\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "快弄完了，沒關係。\n是不是要集合了？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Sagar]"], "content": "<i>已經過了三分鐘喔……忘記時間可不像你的風格。</i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "……慘了……我馬上過去！\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "大 B 你搞什麼啊？全隊集合耶！可以這樣隨便亂晃的嗎？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "你沒資格講他吧。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "抱歉，讓各位久等了……隊長。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "好了，大家都聽我這邊。\n我剛剛接收到總部發來的任務變更指示。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["探勘隊員 T"], "content": "變更？不用緝捕目標了嗎？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "不，緝捕對象不變，但目標狀態由「生死不論」變成「務必活捉」。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "啥！？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……有什麼不滿嗎，Alex？\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "開玩笑！這樣不就不有趣了嗎？\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "……隊長，以目標的危險度來看，活捉的難度遠比射殺更高。這樣一來，緝捕戰略需要重新調整。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["探勘隊員 K"], "content": "我同意，鐘錶店老闆的情報顯示，目標位在封鎖區深處，光是過去就要兩周……環境已經很危險，還得想辦法活捉嗎？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "我明白會增加負擔，不過各位都是 Eagle-01 的菁英，相信不會被難倒的。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "省省吧，斑比！這種無聊的任務，我要退出！\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "豺狼！\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "不要緊，Lucy。\n……Alex，活捉目標的方針不會改變，但我有個任務想交給你。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "啊？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "只要找到人，無論目標有沒有警覺……你直接將他的右手徹底破壞。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "……哦……\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "同時，Lucy 會用電擊彈讓他的右眼短路。失去一半視野和右臂，平衡感會錯亂，那傢伙就無法行動自如。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "這樣的話，弄傷他也無所謂吧？\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "嗯。無所謂。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "……嘿嘿，你是真的想抓到那傢伙？\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "當然。\n如何？接還是不接？\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "廢話！這任務是我的了！\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "很好，我們來討論一下行動細節。\n其他人先回自己的崗位吧。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "……很奇怪啊。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "會嗎？隊長的安排很正確……\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "我是說你。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "……我？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "隊長宣布指令時，大家都很驚訝，只有你一臉平靜，像是早就知道總部的意思一樣。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "……妳想多了。\n我從一開始就覺得這次追緝不單純。讓 A.R.C. 最精銳的我們全隊出動，只為了緝捕一個逃犯？背後的原因肯定不單純。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "所以，你早就預想到可能會發生這種狀況？\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "我好歹也是隊長的頭號參謀呢。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "妳是為了 Sagar 才這麼警戒的吧？放心，在妳還沒入隊時，我、Alex 和他就已經是搭檔了。哈哈……真是懷念。\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "他跟我說過豺狼的事。\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "那妳真該聽聽後面的故事……Sagar 應該很樂意講給妳聽，畢竟他那麼中意妳。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "……作為隊員的話。\n不打擾你了。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Scan_01", "신호 전송"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Sagar]"], "content": "<i>응답하라, B. 지금 뭐 하는 중이지?</i>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "......아, 대장?\n별건 아니고, 오래된 코드를 분석하고 있었어.\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Sagar]"], "content": "<i>도움이 필요한가? \n인력이 필요하면 바로......</i>\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "아, 괜찮아. 거의 다 됐으니까.\n이제 집합 시간인가?\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Sagar]"], "content": "<i>벌써 3분이나 지났다고...\n시간을 까먹는 건 좀처럼 하지 않던 짓이면서.</i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "......이런......지금 바로 합류할게!\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "B 형 대체 뭘 하는 거야? 전대원 소집 시간이잖아! 이렇게 제멋대로면 어떡하냐고!\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "너가 그런 말 할 자격은 없지 않나?\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "미안하다, 모두들, 그리고 대장... 기다리게 해서...\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "좋아. 모두들 잘 들어.\n방금 본부로부터 임무 변경 지시가 내려졌어.\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["탐사대원 T"], "content": "변경? 타깃을 체포할 필요가 없다는 건가?\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "아니, 타깃 체포는 변함 없다. 하지만 타깃에 대한 [생사 불문] 체포에서 [반드시 생포]로 바뀌었을 뿐.\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "뭐어어어!?\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......무슨 불만이라도, Alex? \n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "웃기는 소리 집어치우라고 해!\n그럼 재미 없어지잖아!\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "......대장, 타깃의 위험 수위를 봤을 땐, 생포하는 일은 제거하는 것보다 훨씬 더 힘들어. 만약 그렇게 해야만 한다면 작전을 다시 조정해야 할 필요가 있어.\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["탐사대원 K"], "content": "동의한다. 시계집 사장의 정보에 의하면, 타깃은 현재 봉쇄구역 깊은 곳에 있다고는 하는데, 거기까지 가려면 2주는 걸릴 테니... 거기 환경도 굉장히 위험한데, 그런 곳에서 생포까지 하라니?\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "나도 부담이 상당히 늘어났다는 거, 잘 알고 있다. 하지만 너희들은 모두 Eagle-01 소대의 정예 요원, 잘 해낼 거라고 믿고 있어.\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "하아, 제발 밤비! 이런 시시껄렁한 임무에서 나 좀 빼주면 안 될까?\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "울프!!\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "진정해, Lucy.\n......Alex. 타깃의 생포 방침은 바꿀 수 없지만, 다른 임무를 네게 맡기고 싶어.\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "응?\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "타깃을 발견하는 즉시, 타깃이 눈치를 채든 말든 곧바로 녀석의 오른팔을 파괴해줬으면 해.\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "......오오오....\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "동시에, Lucy.\n너는 전기 충격기로 타깃 오른쪽 눈 회로에 전류를 내보내 줘. 절반의 시야와 오른쪽 팔을 못쓰게 만든다면, 분명 균형 감각이 무너지는 건 순식간일 거야. \n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "그렇다면, 녀석을 다치게 해도 상관없다는 말이지?\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "응, 상관없어.\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "......헤헤헤, 정말 진심으로 그 녀석을 잡고 싶긴 한가 보네?\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "물론이지.\n어때? 할 거야 말 거야?\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "그걸 말이라고!\n그 임무는 내게 맡겨 달라고!\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "좋아, 그럼 다음 작전에 대해 다시 브리핑을 해보자고.\n다른 대원들은 우선 자기 위치로 돌아가도록.\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "발걸음"], "content": ""}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "......이상해.\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "그래? 확실히 대장이 배정한 임무 분담은 나도 조금은...\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "널 말하는 거야.\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "......나?\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "대장이 임무 변동에 관한 사항을 말했을 때, 모두가 놀라고 있는데 너 혼자만 안색이 안 바뀌더군. 꼭 본부에서 어떤 결정을 내릴지 미리 알고 있던 것처럼 말이야.\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "......그건 너무 나갔어.\n난 애초부터 이번 임무가 그저 단순히 범죄자를 체포하는 일이라고 생각한 적 없어. A.R.C.의 최정예 부대가 전부 출동한다니, 고작 탈주범 한 명을 잡기 위해서? 이 배후에는 분명 복잡한 원인들이 얽혀있을 거야.\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "그래서, 처음부터 이런 상황이 일어날 걸 알고 있었단 얘기야?\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "어쨌든 나는 대장의 참모이기도 하니까.\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "Sagar를 위해서 이렇게까지 경계하고 있는 거지? 안심해. 네가 입대하기 전부터, 나랑 Alex, 그리고 저 녀석 셋이 함께 팀이었거든. 하하하... 정말 그때가 그리워지는군.\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "울프 얘기는 들었었는데.\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "그럼 그 후의 얘기도 들어보라고....Sagar도 분명 네게 얘기해주고 싶어 할 거다. 그 녀석도 널 꽤 마음에 들어 하니까.\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "......대원으로써 그렇게 생각하는 거겠지.\n그럼 난 이만.\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "발걸음"], "content": ""}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Scan_01", "訊號傳輸"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Sagar]"], "content": "<i>呼叫大 B。你在做什麼？</i>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "……啊，隊長？\n沒什麼，我在分析一些舊編碼。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Sagar]"], "content": "<i>需要幫忙嗎？我可以安排人手……</i>\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "快弄完了，沒關係。\n是不是要集合了？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Sagar]"], "content": "<i>已經過了三分鐘喔……忘記時間可不像你的風格。</i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "……慘了……我馬上過去！\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "大 B 你搞什麼啊？全隊集合耶！可以這樣隨便亂晃的嗎？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "你沒資格講他吧。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "抱歉，讓各位久等了……隊長。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "好了，大家都聽我這邊。\n我剛剛接收到總部發來的任務變更指示。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["探勘隊員 T"], "content": "變更？不用緝捕目標了嗎？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "不，緝捕對象不變，但目標狀態由「生死不論」變成「務必活捉」。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "啥！？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……有什麼不滿嗎，Alex？\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "開玩笑！這樣不就不有趣了嗎？\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "……隊長，以目標的危險度來看，活捉的難度遠比射殺更高。這樣一來，緝捕戰略需要重新調整。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["探勘隊員 K"], "content": "我同意，鐘錶店老闆的情報顯示，目標位在封鎖區深處，光是過去就要兩周……環境已經很危險，還得想辦法活捉嗎？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "我明白會增加負擔，不過各位都是 Eagle-01 的菁英，相信不會被難倒的。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "省省吧，斑比！這種無聊的任務，我要退出！\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "豺狼！\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "不要緊，Lucy。\n……Alex，活捉目標的方針不會改變，但我有個任務想交給你。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "啊？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "只要找到人，無論目標有沒有警覺……你直接將他的右手徹底破壞。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "……哦……\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "同時，Lucy 會用電擊彈讓他的右眼短路。失去一半視野和右臂，平衡感會錯亂，那傢伙就無法行動自如。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "這樣的話，弄傷他也無所謂吧？\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "嗯。無所謂。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "……嘿嘿，你是真的想抓到那傢伙？\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "當然。\n如何？接還是不接？\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "廢話！這任務是我的了！\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "很好，我們來討論一下行動細節。\n其他人先回自己的崗位吧。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "……很奇怪啊。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "會嗎？隊長的安排很正確……\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "我是說你。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "……我？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "隊長宣布指令時，大家都很驚訝，只有你一臉平靜，像是早就知道總部的意思一樣。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "……妳想多了。\n我從一開始就覺得這次追緝不單純。讓 A.R.C. 最精銳的我們全隊出動，只為了緝捕一個逃犯？背後的原因肯定不單純。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "所以，你早就預想到可能會發生這種狀況？\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "我好歹也是隊長的頭號參謀呢。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "妳是為了 Sagar 才這麼警戒的吧？放心，在妳還沒入隊時，我、Alex 和他就已經是搭檔了。哈哈……真是懷念。\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "他跟我說過豺狼的事。\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "那妳真該聽聽後面的故事……Sagar 應該很樂意講給妳聽，畢竟他那麼中意妳。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "……作為隊員的話。\n不打擾你了。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Scan_01", "讯号传输"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Sagar]"], "content": "<i>呼叫大 B。你在做什么？ </i>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "……啊，队长？\n没什么，我在分析一些旧编码。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Sagar]"], "content": "<i>需要帮忙吗？我可以安排人手……</i>\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "快弄完了，没关系。\n是不是要集合了？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Sagar]"], "content": "<i>已经过了三分钟喔……忘记时间可不像你的风格。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "……惨了……我马上过去！\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快转»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "大 B 你搞什么啊？全队集合耶！可以这样随便乱晃的吗？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "你没资格讲他吧。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "抱歉，让各位久等了……队长。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "好了，大家都听我这边。\n我刚刚接收到总部发来的任务变更指示。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["探勘队员 T"], "content": "变更？不用缉捕目标了吗？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "不，缉捕对象不变，但目标状态由「生死不论」变成「务必活捉」。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "啥！ ？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……有什么不满吗，Alex？\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "开玩笑！这样不就不有趣了吗？\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "……队长，以目标的危险度来看，活捉的难度远比射杀更高。这样一来，缉捕战略需要重新调整。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["探勘队员 K"], "content": "我同意，钟表店老板的情报显示，目标位在封锁区深处，光是过去就要两周……环境已经很危险，还得想办法活捉吗？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "我明白会增加负担，不过各位都是 Eagle-01 的菁英，相信不会被难倒的。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "省省吧，斑比！这种无聊的任务，我要退出！\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "豺狼！\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "不要紧，Lucy。\n……Alex，活捉目标的方针不会改变，但我有个任务想交给你。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "啊？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "只要找到人，无论目标有没有警觉……你直接将他的右手彻底破坏。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "……哦……\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "同时，Lucy 会用电击弹让他的右眼短路。失去一半视野和右臂，平衡感会错乱，那家伙就无法行动自如。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "这样的话，弄伤他也无所谓吧？\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "嗯。无所谓。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "……嘿嘿，你是真的想抓到那家伙？\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "当然。\n如何？接还是不接？\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "废话！这任务是我的了！\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "很好，我们来讨论一下行动细节。\n其他人先回自己的岗位吧。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "脚步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "……很奇怪啊。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "会吗？队长的安排很正确……\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "我是说你。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "……我？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "队长宣布指令时，大家都很惊讶，只有你一脸平静，像是早就知道总部的意思一样。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "……妳想多了。\n我从一开始就觉得这次追缉不单纯。让 A.R.C. 最精锐的我们全队出动，只为了缉捕一个逃犯？背后的原因肯定不单纯。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "所以，你早就预想到可能会发生这种状况？\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "我好歹也是队长的头号参谋呢。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "妳是为了 Sagar 才这么警戒的吧？放心，在妳还没入队时，我、Alex 和他就已经是搭档了。哈哈……真是怀念。\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "他跟我说过豺狼的事。\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "那妳真该听听后面的故事……Sagar 应该很乐意讲给妳听，毕竟他那么中意妳。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "……作为队员的话。\n不打扰你了。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "脚步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[讯号中断]</i>\n"}]]}